16: /// Initializes all required services when WorkManager runs in a background
17: /// isolate (i.e., after the app has been killed). In that scenario [main] is
18: /// never called, so Firebase, Hive, and the notification plugin must be set
19: /// up before any task handler runs.
20: Future<void> _initializeBackgroundServices() async {
21:   try {
